# ExamSpark Tech Stack Rule

Full spec: [`TECH_STACK.md`](TECH_STACK.md) · [`PROJECT_CORE_RULES.md`](PROJECT_CORE_RULES.md)

## Hard Rules

- **Temp delete after processing:** Raw audio (never permanent), temp AI/OCR, upload cache
- **R2:** Large files + exports + **temp audio staging only** — see [`DATA_STORAGE_POLICY.md`](DATA_STORAGE_POLICY.md)
- **R2 permanent:** Full notes `.md`, clean transcript, original PDF/image, OCR, exports — **not** Flashcards/Quiz JSON
- **Supabase:** Structured JSON (Flashcards, Quiz, extras), metadata, short notes (target), pgvector, chat/analytics
- **Postgres:** Never large binaries — structured/searchable data + R2 path references
- **RAG priority (mandatory):** Notes → Transcript (clean) → Teacher Shared → Web
- **Vectors only:** Clean Transcript chunks + Notes + Teacher Shared Notes
- **Backend target:** FastAPI (Python) on Railway with **Docker from day 1**
- **RAG:** pgvector on Supabase PostgreSQL
- **Queue + Cache:** Redis
- **Auth:** Supabase Auth (email, Google; Apple future)
- **Flutter:** `examspark_frontend/lib/` only — Android + Web now; iOS structure ready, App Store later
- **Transcript saved in User Library** — users re-read original explanation; **raw audio deleted** after processing (optional save-audio = future)
- **R2 layout:** `Users/` · `Library/` · `Teachers/` · `Exports/` — see [`TECH_STACK.md`](TECH_STACK.md)
- **Teacher platform:** business dashboard + student access logic — [`TEACHER_PLATFORM.md`](TEACHER_PLATFORM.md)

## User Library UI

```text
📁 Subject (e.g. Physics) → Lecture 12 → Transcript | Notes | Summary
```

## RAG Pipeline Order

1. **Notes** (pgvector) — primary
2. **Clean Transcript** (pgvector) — fallback for detail
3. **Web Search** (Tavily) — last resort

Library read (Transcript/Notes/Summary) = free. Ask AI = credits.

## AI Pipeline

| Step | Model / Service |
|------|-----------------|
| Speech | Groq Whisper Large v3 Turbo → fallback Whisper Large v3 |
| LLM | Qwen 3 Instruct |
| Vision | Qwen3-VL |
| Web search | Tavily API (future: own pipeline) |

## Interim Code (do not extend without reason)

- `examspark_backend/functions/process-lecture/index.ts` — migrate to FastAPI
- Supabase `temp-audio` bucket — migrate to R2

New features: align with FastAPI + R2 + Redis unless founder explicitly keeps edge function.

## Hosting

- MVP: Railway (Docker) + Cloudflare Pages (Flutter Web) + Cloudflare CDN/DNS
- Scale: Hetzner/Contabo VPS, self-hosted Redis, own Qwen GPU server

## Payments & Observability

- India: Razorpay | International: Stripe (future)
- FCM notifications | PostHog analytics | Sentry + Better Stack monitoring
- Admin: Flutter Web (same design)
